==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Autotype
<hw>Au"to*type</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Auto-</ets>
+ <ets>-type</ets>: cf. F. <ets>autotype</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>A facsimile.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A photographic picture produced in sensitized
pigmented gelatin by exposure to light under a negative; and subsequent
washing out of the soluble parts; a kind of picture in ink from a
gelatin plate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Autotypography</ent>⟦br⟧
